.TH timing_allow_input_delay_on_clock_source  22.14 "Fri Oct 06 02:12:27 2023" 
.SH Name \fBtiming_allow_input_delay_on_clock_source\fR
.SH Syntax  \fBtiming_allow_input_delay_on_clock_source\fR  {true | false} 
.P Default: false
.P When set to true, this global variable allows the software to apply input delay constraints on a pin where a clock was previously asserted.
.P To set this global variable, use the set_global command.
